            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> Lizardfolk vanguards use shock tactics to eliminate the most threatening opponents first.<br/><b>Base Statistics</b> When he\u2019s not raging, the vanguard\u2019s statistics are <b>AC</b> 19, touch 12, flat-footed 17; <b>hp</b> 27; <b>Fort </b>+7, <b>Will </b>+1; <b>Melee </b>mwk morningstar +6 (1d8+3), bite +3 (1d6+1) or claw +5 (1d4+3), bite +3 (1d6+1); <b>Str </b>17, <b>Con </b>15; <b>CMB </b>+5; <b>Skills </b>Swim +16."
        },
